{"tid":1425732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蕭若元：中共行動升級L1 濫暴","createTime":"2019-08-06T20:07:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T05:14:28.000Z","uid":282328,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0268e7feda73a32bb504b27c4f5a10e200b19454","tid":1425732,"uid":282328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:07:17.000Z","msg":"[小妹淺見 有錯請大大力屌] <br />\n<br />\n反送中運動能夠行到今時今日因爲大家學識<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">be water 見招拆招</span></span> 認為蕭蕭既評論未嘗不值得參巧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nRjeA1v0k3g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnRjeA1v0k3g&d=%2FAyHQi%2FQiMXiPJLA4RPCZgKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=4f522be2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nRjeA1v0k3g</a><br />\n<br />\n佢係評論中有提到 黑警濫權、過份武力鎮壓、官警黑勾結都係支共第一步棋 亦<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">預測未來黑警三個星期內會拉多600-700個我地寶貴既手足交貨</span></span>（蕭言<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警方每個星期都有target quota</span></span> 所以一到周未就會<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">無差別 亂尻咁拉人</span></span>）以製造恐慌<br />\n<br />\n再加上狗方宜家日撚日開記招 為免有位比狗入抹黑試圖拉攏民意 有小妹認為未來數星期<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非係時候全面進場 勇武既手足中場休息 </span></span> <br />\n<br />\n雖然我地係唔撚怕死 但係為左運動既可持續性 我地要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">減少更多可避免、不必要既犧牲</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e91bd43e2060fa66d35ce013a59b7626225e9845","tid":1425732,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:16:37.000Z","msg":"咁即係暫時唔會點拉人,義士好安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d93cb2eafb37f7b8f85d205989c79b6e4d703e99","tid":1425732,"uid":261396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:17:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"660289c136e8c99bdb53ec1c3cade424aa57a1ae","tid":1425732,"uid":282328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:43:41.000Z","msg":"已經接近300位義士被捕 不明不白呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e84e01c5595c694c17beddda4ae6dc4084c28dfa","tid":1425732,"uid":5489,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:46:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0f1c05f212aef5d93a96b0542572f85b37485ea","tid":1425732,"uid":5489,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e84e01c5595c694c17beddda4ae6dc4084c28dfa","tid":1425732,"uid":5489,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:46:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:46:36.000Z","msg":"行得正但得正一樣拉得"},{"pid":"682917bea48e95469559194807932473b0a955c0","tid":1425732,"uid":282328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e84e01c5595c694c17beddda4ae6dc4084c28dfa","tid":1425732,"uid":5489,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:46:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:59:11.000Z","msg":"已經賣左兩個月喇 雖然要得到一啲野就要犧牲一啲野 但係係咪盲目犧牲就係最好呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔可以當對手係傻系"},{"pid":"06d96c4e09f1890e517439ba023b30f30b7acd87","tid":1425732,"uid":282328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:56:40.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"p